Caledonia Investments, reported a 26 per cent advance in pre-tax profits
from Pounds 3.74m to Pounds 4.71m for the year ended March 31.
Turnover for the company, of which Cayzer Trust holds 48.8 per cent and
Caledonia has a stake of 21.05 per cent, expanded to Pounds 47m, compared
