<PROFILE>_AN-EFVDUACWFT</PROFILE>
<DATE>940622
</DATE>
<HEADLINE>
FT  22 JUN 94 / People: JP Morgan
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Alex Pilato, a vice-president of JP Morgan, has been appointed head of risk
management advisory services within HSBC's treasury and capital markets
division.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>HSBC Holdings.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
